lass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ea2678d9f0a07245749217e5416cdc32059f2f","tid":1984833,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:56:06.000Z","msg":"我日日reweet嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c8a8488196867fb44e44e0444435804baebc0c","tid":1984833,"uid":320192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42ea2678d9f0a07245749217e5416cdc32059f2f","tid":1984833,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:56:06.000Z","msg":"我日日reweet嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:56:46.000Z","msg":"愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a676e20b0f13f8d33039cd06b454325420e5ce90","tid":1984833,"uid":213037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:45:23.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線手足整咗個網站出嚟比大家做task<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後大家無藉口唔打國際線喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲bookmark 佢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Ftwitter&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=9d7712b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n<br />\n入bot 拎任務24小時更新：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=1eff7462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n另有手足會係佢Twitter Account 每日更新任務:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTweetingforHK&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=438cec2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK</a><br />\n<br />\n或者download 香城online 個app 都有Twitter 任務做<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKOnlinePortal&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=73441660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal</a><br />\n<br />\nLike retweet reply<br />\nTask2係國際戰線，唔好淨係推Task 1,Task2都好重要。<br />\n*如果見到想用嘅圖已經有手足用咗請搵第二張圖<br />\n*如果見到已經有好多圖就唔好再放圖，只留文字（短短地都得）<br />\n*唔好只係扔低張圖咩字都唔打<br />\n*唔知留咩好就like 手足留言或者啲對我哋有利嘅留言<br />\n<br />\n將Twitter 變成日常，每人每日做少少。<br />\n每人嘅一小步加埋就係一大步。<br />\n我哋唔知做咩先有用，所以咩都試下咩都做下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf189176220f7268bade8d0967857253e03afd5f","tid":1984833,"uid":88394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:24:10.000Z","msg":"我開左a/c 差唔多有8年都係得幾個followers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋都仲係唔係幾識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0843d9b3d9fdbd86b2bdfe378ec16b06c20f085","tid":1984833,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:25:54.000Z","msg":"因為一開始少人follow<br />\n無令人覺得做咗野但無咩效果"},{"pid":"7f1297710e71c3aa6dfe77076b8c47f20cc29f52","tid":1984833,"uid":320192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0843d9b3d9fdbd86b2bdfe378ec16b06c20f085","tid":1984833,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:25:54.000Z","msg":"因為一開始少人follow<br />\n無令人覺得做咗野但無咩效果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"Like同tweet同寫下hashtag 都有用！<br />\n大有大做 小有小做 每一part都有佢既作用！"},{"pid":"6b399d8f488eb77ebf778bdb7ca8644df35ddd8b","tid":1984833,"uid":320192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf189176220f7268bade8d0967857253e03afd5f","tid":1984833,"uid":88394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc